openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Title
  description: Title
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https'
paths:
  /v1/{version}/v2/{name}:
    get:
      operationId: "pathParameter"
      parameters:
        - name: version
          in: path
          required: true
          description: test
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - name: name
          in: path
          required: true
          description: test
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ok
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
